Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,--------------正文--------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.63,0:00:16.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.84,0:00:20.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马怎么淋成个落汤鸡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.85,0:00:23.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,半路上下起了大雨…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.44,0:00:25.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  总之先把衣服脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.35,0:00:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然会感冒的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.60,0:00:28.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  把热水准备起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.02,0:00:30.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.56,0:00:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舒服啊舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:48.04,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在态度上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.92,0:00:52.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:56.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.35,0:01:02.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你可可  是热的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.09,0:01:04.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢  春香
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:11.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  冬马  
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.43,0:01:15.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真会添麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.94,0:01:18.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直是全套的国王待遇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.96,0:01:25.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了千秋  借套衣服给我穿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.81,0:01:30.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这什么态度啊  求人的方法就这么一种吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.97,0:01:34.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最会装撒娇的小女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.96,0:01:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  衣服还要等上一段时间才会干
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:38.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.85,0:01:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.67,0:01:44.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件事就交给我来处理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.20,0:01:48.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来纠正冬马的小女儿脾气
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.82,0:01:53.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？嗯…那就拜托你了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.55,0:01:56.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈  藤冈什么时候来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.19,0:01:58.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  藤冈？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.37,0:02:01.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想他就快到了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.34,0:02:03.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  千秋  快把衣服借我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.69,0:02:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直这样下去  有点儿…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.20,0:02:06.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不借
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.93,0:02:07.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.53,0:02:09.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋衣服借来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.87,0:02:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.95,0:02:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是故意找麻烦嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.21,0:02:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来夏树昨天这样说过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:26.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有两把刷子嘛  冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这家伙  看我这招  怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.59,0:02:34.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.64,0:02:37.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真弱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.87,0:02:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马  把那个类似手柄的东西给我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.91,0:02:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.63,0:02:49.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了冬马  再比一次
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.72,0:02:51.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.62,0:02:54.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招  看招  看招  看招…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.14,0:02:57.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招  看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.62,0:03:06.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛结束
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:13.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马  男子汉的恩仇都要双倍奉还
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.25,0:03:20.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以身为男子汉  我要从你那儿把衣服夺走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.58,0:03:21.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,复仇给你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:26.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？只因为你是女生  没衣服穿感到很为难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.09,0:03:30.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了冬马   我的衣服借你穿
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.39,0:03:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋啊  你就借衣服给我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.10,0:03:49.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就  不  借
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.26,0:03:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤脑筋啊  突然下起雨来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.87,0:03:57.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  你好  南同学
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:03:59.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一样啊 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:01.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:04.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.16,0:04:06.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快借给我  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:08.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说不借就不借
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:09.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这件就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.39,0:04:11.13,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.18,0:04:11.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别跑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:14.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  我宰了你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:15.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.34,0:04:17.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.05,0:04:18.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么  冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.89,0:04:19.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.79,0:04:22.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你了  千秋大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.88,0:04:25.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借衣服给我吧  我知错了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.71,0:04:29.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～好孩子  还是会求人的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.10,0:04:31.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我房间来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.10,0:04:34.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好求你就行了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.23,0:04:39.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.28,0:04:40.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:42.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也别当没事儿人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.32,0:04:45.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之要注意态度哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:50.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.52,0:04:54.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.60,0:05:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香都欢迎你了  你这什么态度啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.23,0:05:01.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.15,0:05:04.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得了  藤冈也一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.87,0:05:08.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快脱了快脱了  总之先泡个澡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.91,0:05:11.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到…到底是何事啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.95,0:06:49.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这糖真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟宝石一样  红艳艳的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.24,0:06:55.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是红啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.29,0:07:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些天然色素是提取虫子的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点儿  内田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.64,0:07:15.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会有问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.94,0:07:17.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…大概
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.23,0:07:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.20,0:07:25.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个由你自己处理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.75,0:07:34.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  吐出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分  千秋就会拿高深的知识来伤人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  说一个不伤人的高深的知识来听听
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:46.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.41,0:07:48.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说到虫子…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:51.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  黑大蚁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.26,0:07:59.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在初春五六月雨后的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.83,0:08:02.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长着翅膀的雌雄黑大蚁
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会飞出巢穴在空中进行结婚飞行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.47,0:08:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.12,0:08:08.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.64,0:08:13.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我在听  但还要继续吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:32.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在空中举行婚礼  这是多么美好的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:37.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？  说完了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.84,0:08:41.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  公主的兴致受到严重打击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.92,0:08:45.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因为…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.44,0:08:48.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说一个关于千秋的高深的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.70,0:08:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别人不认真听她说话就会生气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.89,0:08:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好普通
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.73,0:09:01.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便说一个关于我的高深的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.33,0:09:03.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光凭按门铃的方式  我就能听出门外是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:04.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.59,0:09:09.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个声音是…吉野来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:10.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉野吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.63,0:09:22.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我说是藤冈来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.60,0:09:23.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,造谣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:29.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.19,0:09:31.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.09,0:09:41.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋  快看外面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.48,0:09:53.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞机云啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:10:00.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋难不成想用高深的知识伤害我喜欢的藤冈吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.22,0:10:01.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:09.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飞机云大多是废气在空中迅速冷却凝聚而成的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:12.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并非烟雾而是真正的云哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.60,0:10:15.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人工云
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:29.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:33.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么尽冲着我说些讨厌的话题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.06,0:10:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这气氛算什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:40.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,内田  那不是空气是飞机云
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.01,0:10:40.30,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（「空気」在日语中有气氛和空气两种意思）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.50,0:10:43.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  不是指那个空气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.59,0:10:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快看  是废气
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.41,0:10:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了是云
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:08.26,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次休假和春香姐姐  夏奈一起去百货商场了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.39,0:11:11.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么一到休假就会有作业呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.50,0:11:09.87,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:13.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:14.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很开心  还吃三色豆了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.54,0:11:17.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唯一知道的就是不懂这些问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.71,0:11:16.59,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是忘不了那个味道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:19.51,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天气好才觉得更加美味了吧 
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.71,0:11:20.21,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.58,0:11:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋真是喜欢藤冈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.59,0:11:22.80,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能尝到就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:25.35,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.43,0:11:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.52,0:11:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他都已经成了千秋的指定席了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样也罢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.58,0:11:39.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚认识藤冈的时候  他害得我够呛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.70,0:11:44.66,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（刚认识不久）
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.82,0:11:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对  那是352阵型
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.63,0:11:51.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么傻话呢  看那个画面绝对是361
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:55.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还可以增加前锋摆成343阵型哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.86,0:11:59.60,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样前锋是不是太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.03,0:12:01.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈这是怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.83,0:12:04.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是在你换衣服的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:07.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马和藤冈关于足球趣味相投而聊上了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:09.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.52,0:12:16.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,踢的最精彩的一幕是长传之后两人配合拉出空位
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.13,0:12:21.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起这个  怕是没人料到之前会传出那一记穿越球
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.50,0:12:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本听不懂在聊什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:28.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之这意见交换得很快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.30,0:12:31.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.83,0:12:34.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.74,0:12:35.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂停一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.07,0:12:36.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:40.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会儿要记得补时哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:41.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.69,0:12:45.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.25,0:12:48.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  那个…对了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:52.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对藤冈自我介绍了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.66,0:12:54.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:12:58.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.14,0:13:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫冬马  担任前锋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.39,0:13:06.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫藤冈  任何位置都能踢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.28,0:13:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任何位置？  好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:09.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过奖
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:12.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厉害啊  真的好厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.52,0:13:15.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.96,0:13:17.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂停
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:18.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.92,0:13:21.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏奈记一下补时时间
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.43,0:13:22.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.88,0:13:24.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:29.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  把你的性别告诉藤冈了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.85,0:13:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马不久前刚成为千秋的弟弟
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.07,0:13:35.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.67,0:13:37.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说了没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.10,0:13:41.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没特意去提过…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:44.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好冬马  在藤冈面前你就当男生
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.23,0:13:48.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易在足球方面能聊得那么投机
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.62,0:13:51.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个男子汉友好地踢球…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:54.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  怎么了千秋？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.67,0:13:55.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天你很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.79,0:13:58.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点儿都不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.04,0:14:05.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之那是我的专座  让开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.01,0:14:07.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.17,0:14:09.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤冈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:15.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是千秋的位置  再过去一点儿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.51,0:14:17.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要说的不是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.93,0:14:20.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  到底想怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.24,0:14:39.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么想打架吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:41.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正合我意啊  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:43.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  住手冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:45.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么  放手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.50,0:14:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能对女生动粗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.16,0:14:49.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:51.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.86,0:14:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎你挺会踢足球  但胸部囤积了过多脂肪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.82,0:15:01.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:02.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.08,0:15:05.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我来锻炼你的身心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.35,0:15:09.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.20,0:15:12.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进行特训吧  冬马
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:14.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.71,0:15:27.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…所以那是中央过人之后凌空抽射
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.36,0:15:28.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过人？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.21,0:15:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么刚才的防卫中缝又是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:35.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那应该叫防卫中锋  千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.92,0:15:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这类话题冬马不是很了解的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.26,0:15:41.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来  冬马今天没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和冬马之间发生什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:47.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.76,0:15:55.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了冬马？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:58.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.28,0:16:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特训害的啊特训
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.99,0:16:02.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一大早就被叫醒出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:05.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  这算什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.36,0:16:10.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋的弟弟  足球少年吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.51,0:16:13.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.49,0:16:17.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就别去特训了  怎么你反倒变温顺了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.38,0:16:22.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  对了  下次千秋也来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:26.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我积了脂肪再去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.16,0:16:32.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,于是  春香姐姐在百货商店…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.75,0:16:33.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.48,0:16:35.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是够呛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.86,0:16:40.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之后晨练又持续了一段时间
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.34,0:16:41.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终千秋还是没来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋不擅长运动嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.30,0:16:50.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也是没办法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.83,0:16:52.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.14,0:18:36.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏树  有事拜托别人时  这样措辞可不好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.87,0:18:39.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在外面可是有模有样的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.55,0:18:40.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:43.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一不小心就会露出马脚的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.80,0:18:44.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.45,0:18:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边的南家  非常重礼仪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有那张脸孔不怎么好看呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.94,0:18:52.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的脸不都差不多吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.91,0:18:54.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  是你眼神之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.87,0:18:57.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么看都没有求别人的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:18:59.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容  露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:02.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是措辞和笑容啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:09.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不是很懂  但有事求春香要小心的是千秋
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:12.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搭理千秋虽然很麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.96,0:19:15.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但如果无视她会给春香留下坏印象
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.16,0:19:17.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别无视她啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:19.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋是那个扎辫子的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:20.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是夏奈
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.09,0:19:25.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟她扯上关系情况就复杂了  尽量避开她为妙  
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.01,0:19:26.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然这样很不好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.68,0:19:41.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,措辞和笑容…吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.20,0:19:47.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下今日到访有一事相求
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.82,0:19:54.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小小意思  不成敬意
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.30,0:20:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  千秋  馒头能有这个意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.01,0:20:05.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多半是蒸过的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.61,0:20:10.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于冬马的事有事相求
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:14.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊  也只有冬马的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.73,0:20:17.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑容笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:31.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为冬马回家有些晚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.04,0:20:35.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想请你们加以教导
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.57,0:20:38.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚…刚才冷笑了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:41.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们有对冬马说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.44,0:20:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟夏奈扯上关系情况就复杂了  尽量避开她为妙 
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.11,0:20:49.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  说过没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:03.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  光知道看春香
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.10,0:21:06.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春香姐姐被他盯上了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.63,0:21:08.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不同意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对冬马说过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.49,0:21:22.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果无视千秋会给春香留下坏印象
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.47,0:21:24.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别无视她
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.13,0:21:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你对冬马说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.23,0:21:39.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然说过了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.90,0:21:42.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直是置若罔闻完全不当回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.23,0:21:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再严厉管教一下不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.94,0:22:01.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再严厉管教一下不就行了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.28,0:22:04.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经严厉管教过了  结果还是行不通
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.09,0:22:10.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  听到我说话了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.75,0:22:20.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此  我和她谈谈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.30,0:22:22.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:27.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冬马  今后早点儿回家怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.29,0:22:41.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然春香都那么说了  就这么做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.08,0:22:52.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后达成协议提早半个小时回来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.48,0:22:56.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错吧  措辞果然很重要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.65,0:22:58.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  还是笑容比较重要
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.55,0:23:00.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  是措辞…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.57,0:23:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  是笑容…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.78,0:23:06.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求人就是为了让我早点儿回家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.55,0:23:11.55,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（第二天  傍晚）
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.79,0:23:21.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问  打扰一下
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.85,0:23:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是微不足道
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.58,0:23:25.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这莴苣能再便宜一些吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.87,0:23:33.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千秋多谢相助  谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.43,0:23:35.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就这样说不就行了  蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:37.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常危险啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.72,0:23:39.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一回  南家三姐妹～欢迎回来～
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.11,0:23:41.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好印象
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.36,0:23:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事儿人一样是指什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.25,0:23:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
